review_description: Gunung Mas : Kabin bisa muat 6 org (kami isi 4 sih), tapi kapasitas pemanas air hanya utk 2 dewasa, setelah itu perlu tunggu 90 menit utk pemanasan berikutnya. Seharusnya kapasitas pemanas air disesuaikan dgn kapasitas kabin, krn ini daerag dingin, otomatis semua org mau mandi air hangat. Shower mandi airnya kecil, dan drain hole kamar mandi airnya super slow jd menggenang lama, payah.
review_description_en: Gunung Mas: Cabin can fit 6 people (we fill 4 anyway), but the water heater capacity is only for 2 adults, after that we need to wait 90 minutes for the next heating. The water heater capacity should be adjusted to the capacity of the cabin, because this is cold, automatically all people want to take a warm bath. The shower of the shower is small, and drain the bathroom hole is super slow water so long, bad.

review_description: Hotel jelek dengan pelayanan ramah : Kita ngga bisa milih siapa yang menginap di pods atas/bawah kita. Kebanyakan sih orang orang norak yang baru punya duit dan merasa mereka bayar dan berhak jadi raja. Ngobrolnya berisik, dengerin lagu keras keras dan aktivitas dalam pods ganggu karena berisik. Sudah dikomplain tp cuma diiyakan dan ngga ada teguran langsung. Cuma "maaf segera kami telusuri." dan "baik, mohon ditunggu". Halah.
review_description_en: Ugly hotel with friendly service: we can't choose who is staying at our upper/lower pods. Most of the tacky people who just have money and feel they pay and have the right to become kings. The chat is noisy, listen to hard songs and the activities in Pods are disturbed because they are noisy. Already complained but only agreed and there is no direct reprimand. Just "sorry we immediately traced." And "Good, please wait". Halah.
